recognized open source license by the Open Source Initiative:
http://opensource.org/licenses/LPL-1.02

The zlib/libpng license is a recognized "\"free\"" software license by the
Free Software Foundation: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/license-list.html#lucent102
However, the FSF doesn't like it and says it's incompatible with their preferred
licenses.
